Title: Stochastic Variational Approach to Minimum Uncertainty States
Authors: F. Illuminati and L. Viola
Comments: 11 pages, latex, 12pt A4wide, no figures
Report-no: DFPD 94/TH/67, December 1994
Journal-ref: J.Phys. A28 (1995) 2953-2962
\\
We introduce a new variational characterization of Gaussian diffusion processes
as minimum uncertainty states. We then define a variational method constrained
by kinematics of diffusions and Schr\"{o}dinger dynamics to seek states of
local minimum uncertainty for general non-harmonic potentials.
